IMPORTANT DISCLAIMER:

This software is designed for LABORATORY USE ONLY. It is intended for:
- GNSS receiver development and testing
- Indoor laboratory research environments
- Educational purposes

DO NOT USE THIS SOFTWARE:
- Outdoors or in aircraft
- Near airports or aviation facilities  
- In violation of local RF emission regulations
- To interfere with actual GNSS services

REGULATORY COMPLIANCE:
Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with all applicable local, 
national, and international regulations regarding RF emissions and GNSS 
signal transmission. The developers assume no responsibility for any 
interference, violations, or damages resulting from use of this software.

SIGNAL IDENTIFICATION:
All generated signals should be clearly identified as simulated/test signals
and used only in controlled laboratory environments.

